  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I expect that I won't see chat history from deleted 1-1 chat when I start new one.\r\nAs there is no button in 1-1 chat \"delete history\" - so I expect that chat history will be deleted as chat itself.\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\n1-1 Chat history is uploaded when start new chat after deleting it \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nNew chat is started with no chat history.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nAfter deleting 1-1 chat and starting new chat with the same user - chat history appeares in new chat.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Tap on Start new chart\r\n- Send anyone from contacts several messages and recieve some\r\n- Delete chat\r\n- Start new chat again\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version:  2018/03/06 03:19:52 UTC\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Android",
